name: gdk_pixbuf
deps: glib, libjpeg_turbo, libpng, shared_mime_info, libsvg, libtiff, corg_libraries
desc:
The Gdk Pixbuf package is a toolkit for image loading and pixel 
buffer manipulation. It is used by GTK+ 2 and GTK+ 3 to load and 
manipulate images. In the past it was distributed as part of GTK+ 2 
but it was split off into a separate package in preparation 
for the change to GTK+ 3.
